            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p2">快到圣诞，好多朋友都想送一份高贵典雅、又靓又实用的礼物给至爱，或者送一份礼物奖励自己全年工作的努力。丹麦音响品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen (B&amp;O) 创立于 1925 年，作为丹麦王室家族御用品牌，他们一直推出极具品味、型格设计，同时具有专业鉴听级质素的音响产品。今个圣诞想买一部样靓而又好声的喇叭，就要继续留意下面介绍的三款 B&amp;O 精选喇叭产品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208126 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1066" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p class="p2">B&amp;O 在 11 月刚庆祝他们成立 98 周年，这个少数可以经历这份长久岁月的音响品牌，其经典作品曾经被纽约现代艺术博物馆 MoMa 作为永久展品。而面向现代音响科技发展，B&amp;O 结合了经典设计、出色的造工与时尚生活，推出一系列喇叭产品。</p><h2 class="p2">超轻薄设计精致书本扬声器<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>全新 Beosound Emerge</h2><p class="p2">这次重点介绍的是这部 B&amp;O Beosound Emerge 经典款入门级产品。设计用上书本式扁平设计，书脊位置用上铝金属物料，令高级感提升，加上喇叭厚度只有 6.7cm，看上去更像一本书，漫不经意地融入你的生活空间。即使在狭窄的香港居住空间中，仍能突显你的生活品味。放在书架上，它马上就同你的书架融为一体，也可放在厨房的角落、客厅的小桌上。而即使喇叭体积细小，但仍能发出足够声量，让整个房间都被音乐包覆。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-rotated.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209537 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-600x900.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-rotated.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208121 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg" alt="" width="1067" height="1600" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg 1067w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1207764 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">难能可贵的是这个尺寸的喇叭，仍可呈现出极广阔的 180 度音响效果，令整个房间充满音乐。极为轻薄的喇叭机身，Beosound Emerge 融合了由 B&amp;O 工程师精密调整的小型驱动器。驱动器采用特殊设计，包括了底部侧放的 4 吋低音单元、中间倾斜摆放的轻巧型 1.45 吋中音驱动单元，还有装在顶端向正面发声的 0.6 吋高音单元，令喇叭面向任何方位，用家都可获得 180 度全方位音乐体验。用家可连接两部 Beosound Emerge 使用 B&amp;O 智能电话 App 进行立体声配对，享受更广阔音场。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208125 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1229" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-694x533.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-1172x900.jpg 1172w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-768x590.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-1536x1180.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208120 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p class="p2">除了实用好声，B&amp;O 音响品牌更追求产品的耐用程度，Beosound Emerge 提供 3 年官方保养期，产品荣获 Cradle to Cradle Certified 的 Bronze 认证，随著声音技术的不断进化，用户可以在来年乃至未来数十年轻松为该产品升级。采用了尖端数码管理平台 Mozart Platform 的扬声器，确保了扬声器日后升级，可迎合日新月异的全新音乐需求。</p><p class="p2"><strong>B&amp;O Beosound Emerge</strong></p><p class="p2"><strong>建议零售价：HK$5,598（3 年保养期）</strong></p><h2 class="p2">令整个家居变成音乐厅<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>碳黑色第 3 代 Beosound 2</h2><p class="p2">想突显你的生活品味，这部 B&amp;O Beosound 2 3rd Gen 扬声器将成为你家居中一件实用又型格的艺术品。Beosound 2 3rd Gen 家庭扬声器可说是 B&amp;O 标志性产品，在第三代更推出超型格碳黑新款。铝金属外壳，设计优雅之余，支援多房间控制 (Multiroom) 功能，更可 360 度发声，不论摆放在家中任何位置，都可令整个环境变成了广阔的音乐空间。Beosound 2 3rd Gen 同样采用 Mozart Platform 令它日后透过软件升级加入更多新功能。</p><p class="p2"><strong>B&amp;O Beosound 2 第 3 代碳黑色</strong></p><p class="p2"><strong>建议零售价：HK$26,990（3 年保养期）</strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209541 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1920" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg 1067w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209540 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-rotated.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209542 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-rotated.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1920" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-rotated.jpg 1067w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0052-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0001.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209538 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0001.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0001.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0001-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0001-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><h2 class="p2">Beosound A5 便携扬声器太空铝版本</h2><p class="p2">如果你想行到边听到边，就要特别推介这款 B&amp;O Beosound A5 太空铝版本。它便携性非常之强，拥有手抽设计，随时移到家居任何位置以至室外欣赏音乐。它拥有 12 小时续航力让你拿出街可以听一整天。扬声器顶部面板上内置的无线充电功能，更可为你的手机充电，不担心音乐因手机无电而切断。Beosound A5 同样采用 Mozard Platform 可随时为扬声器升级新功能。</p><p class="p2"><strong>B&amp;O Beosound A5 太空铝版本</strong></p><p class="p2"><strong>建议零售价：HK$11,498（3 年保养期）</strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-694x419.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-1280x773.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-768x464.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-1536x927.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">上述介绍 3 款 B&amp;O 喇叭于 K11 MUSEA、ifc mall、铜锣湾专门店，以及指定授权零售商有售。</p><p><span lang="ZH-TW">查询指定授权零售商：</span>3898 4910</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/bang-olufsen-chrismas-2023/wireless-home/">丹麦 B&#038;O 精选品味家居扬声器，今个圣诞送一份超型礼物给至爱</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
