        <item>
            <title>横滨将举办无人机动漫灯光表演　巨型《鬼灭之刃》《新世纪福音战士》角色登场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/stardance-yokohama/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=stardance-yokohama</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/stardance-yokohama/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:57:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[动漫]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无人机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210176</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>无人机除了用来拍照之外，近年也越来越多的灯光表演。最近在横滨就将会举办一场无人机动漫灯光表演，《鬼灭之刃》和《新世纪福音战士》等经典动漫角色也会登场。<br /><span id="more-1210176"></span></p><p>这次的灯光表演 STARDANCE 将会在横滨八景岛 Sea Paradise 举办，从 12 月 23 日至 24 日以及 29 日至 31 日之间 5 日举行，将会用到 1,000 架装有 LED 灯的无人机，在 200 米阔，200 米高的空间中演出不同的动漫角色，包括《新世纪福音战士》、《鬼灭之刃》和《咸蛋超人》等都有。无人机表演每场约 15 分钟，不同的角色和主题分布在不同的时段演出。在 12 月 24 日晚还将举办一场特别的圣诞演出。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69569"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zs4GkrWvX8E?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>STARDANCE 筹备已经历经一年，导演润间大仁表示，STARDANCE 之名源于他首次目睹无人机表演时，有如星星般闪烁的场景。他希望透过这场活动，让参与者感受到兴奋和愉悦的体验。在过去 12 年，无人机的性能大幅提升，表现力和绘制能力也有了显著的进步，令今次的活动得以实现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1210192" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/PH18-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.seaparadise.co.jp/special/stardance/">Stardance</a>, <a href="https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/kikaku/1552661.html">Impress</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/stardance-yokohama/life-tech/travel/">横滨将举办无人机动漫灯光表演　巨型《鬼灭之刃》《新世纪福音战士》角色登场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
