        <item>
            <title>iPhone 15 Pro「空间影片」拍摄功能　可在 Vision Pro 重温</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/spatial-video/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=spatial-video</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/spatial-video/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 12:14:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 17.2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Spatial Video]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[空间影片]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210125</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 推出 iOS 17.2 后，用家可用 iPhone 15 Pro 和 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄「空间影片（Spatial Video）」，而明年初则可在 Apple Vision Pro 上重温立体感十足的日常回忆影片。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210126 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-hero_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲明年初开始，用家可在 Apple Vision Pro 上重温影片。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家只要将 iPhone 15 Pro 和 iPhone 15 Pro Max 更新至 iOS 17.2，即可拍摄空间影片，以 3D 立体捕捉最爱时刻。「空间影片」在标准动态范围内，以 1080p、30 fps 拍摄。使用方法亦很简单，开启「相机」app 的「影片」模式，将 iPhone 转至横向，轻点「空间影片」标志，再轻点「拍摄」。iPhone 会同时以主相机和超广角相机开始拍摄影片，再将超广角相机的视角调整至与主相机一样，然后将两者储存为一个影片档案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210127 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-iPhone-15-Pro-spatial-video-capture-cameras_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「空间影片」以 iPhone 15 Pro 和 iPhone 15 Pro Max 的主相机和超广角相机横向拍摄</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">在 iPhone 和其他装置上，「空间影片」会显示为一般 2D 影片。用家可以在「相片」app 的全新「空间」相簿内，找得所拍摄的「空间影片」；而所有「空间影片」亦可透过 iCloud，在所有装置上同步储存。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2023/12/apple-introduces-spatial-video-capture-on-iphone-15-pro/">Apple </a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/spatial-video/software/ios-app/">iPhone 15 Pro「空间影片」拍摄功能　可在 Vision Pro 重温</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
