        <item>
            <title>Google 败诉　Epic Games 控告 Google Play 垄断市场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/epic-games-2/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=epic-games-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/epic-games-2/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 11:30:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Epic Games]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google play]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210081</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Epic Games 控告 Google Play 垄断了程序分销和支付市场，美国加利福尼亚州联邦陪审团裁定罪成，Google 为上述判决提出异议。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210084 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/epic-games-store-ratings-and-polls-update-1920x1080-dc391bf9ab36-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Epic Games 控告 Google Play 垄断了程序分销和支付市场获胜诉</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">加利福尼亚州陪审团裁定了 Google Play 违反反竞争行为肆意行使垄断权，包括：Google 在 Android 应用分发市场和应用内支付服务市场拥有垄断地位、Google 在市场上用了不正当竞争行为、Google Play 应用商店和 Google 支付服务之间存在非法的捆绑关系和其分销协议、Google 内部项目「Project Hug」，即通过交易要求 20 家开发商不创建与 Google Play 竞争的应用商店，存在不正当竞争行为。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 政府事务和公共政策副总裁 Wilson White 反驳指：「Android 和 Google Play 提供了比任何其他主要移动平台更多的选择和开放性，审判清楚地表明，我们与苹果及其 App Store 以及 Android 设备上的其他应用商店竞争激烈。」</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-67688720">BBC</a>，Epic Games</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/epic-games-2/software/">Google 败诉　Epic Games 控告 Google Play 垄断市场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
